OL,3,C2,000 year-old divination spoon found
OL,4,Cin Isle of Man
OL,6,FA 2,000 year-old spoon believed to
OL,7,Fhave been used for 'telling the
OL,8,Ffuture' has been discovered in the
OL,9,FIsle of Man.
OL,11,FThe bronze spoon, dating back to the
OL,12,FIron Age, has described by
OL,13,Farchaeologists as "one of the most
OL,14,Fintriguing objects ever discovered on
OL,15,Fthe island" and could have been used
OL,16,Ffor "ritual activities".
OL,18,FIt was was found by metal detectorist
OL,19,FRob Middleton on private land in
OL,20,FPatrick, on the west coast.
