OL,3,C2,000 year-old divination spoon found
OL,4,Cin Isle of Man
OL,6,FManx National Heritage said similar
OL,7,Fartefacts have been found in Britain,
OL,8,FIreland and France, but this is only
OL,9,Fthe 28th example discovered worldwide,
OL,10,Fand the first from the Isle of Man.
OL,12,FAllison Fox, Curator for Archaeology
OL,13,Ffor Manx National Heritage said: "Iron
OL,14,FAge finds are relatively scarce, with
OL,15,Fbronze spoons dating to this period
OL,16,Frare, making this find all the more
OL,17,Fremarkable.
