OL,3,C2,000 year-old divination spoon found
OL,4,Cin Isle of Man
OL,6,F"Although it sounds rather plain
OL,7,Fbecause we call it a spoon, it really
OL,8,Fis an unusual find illustrating
OL,9,Fpotential prehistoric ritual activity
OL,10,Ftaking place on the Isle of Man".
OL,12,FThe exact function of the spoon is
OL,13,Funknown, however the leading theory is
OL,14,Fthat it was used in divination rituals
OL,15,Fas our ancestors sought to predict the
OL,16,Ffuture.
