OL,3,C2,000 year-old divination spoon found
OL,4,Cin Isle of Man
OL,6,FAllison said: "The spoons are usually
OL,7,Ffound in pairs, and it has been
OL,8,Fsuggested that liquid of some form
OL,9,Fwould have been poured into the spoon
OL,10,Fwhich has the cross, and whatever
OL,11,Fquarter it landed in would tell
OL,12,Fsomething about the future.
OL,14,F"The details of such ceremonies have
OL,15,Fbeen lost in the midst of time.
