OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F394A1739212694
OL,3,C2,000 year-old divination spoon found
OL,4,Cin Isle of Man
OL,6,F"We are hugely grateful to both Rob
OL,7,Fand David for donating this very
OL,8,Fspecial find. Both have given other
OL,9,Fartefacts over the years to the Manx
OL,10,FNational Collections, and all are now
OL,11,Favailable for further research.
OL,13,F"Donations such as this really help us
OL,14,Fexplore what our ancestors were up to,
OL,15,Fand this find in particular puts the
OL,16,FIsle of Man firmly on the map of Iron
OL,17,FAge ritual".
OL,19,FThe spoon has been donated to the Manx
OL,20,FNational Collections cared for by Manx
OL,21,FNational Heritage at the Manx Museum.
